Description:
Renovated 2 bedroom unit in the heart of Dandenong
This two bedroom plus study unit is set at the rear of a quiet complex and just minutes away from Dandenong Plaza, train station, local schools and it offers easy access to all amenities. Featuring:
- 2 spacious bedrooms plus study and master with double BIR's
- Spacious kitchen and dining area
- Generous sized living room with gas heating
Relax with a walk in the park located a footstep away from your own backyard and overlooking a tranquil reserve. With refurbished roofing plumbing and a single lock-up garage to complete the picture this is a mixture of convenience and relaxed lifestyle that is not to be missed!

Description:
PREMIUM & SPACIOUS 4 BEDROOM FAMILY LIVING IN GREAT LOCATION
Low maintenance living does not have to mean small. Young & modern, this bright & Spacious townhouse promises premium family living close to central Shopping, Chisolm TAFE as well as primary and secondary schools, hospital and Dandenongs Oasis centre.
Enjoy generous zoned family living including formal lounge to the front of the home whilst a large meals/dining area is adjacent a state of the art kitchen with walk in pantry and quality stainless steel appointments showcased beneath ceasar-stone benchtops that also feature in the 3 fully appointed bathrooms and fitted-laundry with external access.
A bright and sunny family room is adjacent meals/dining and looks out over the neat garden/courtyard. Remote control garage enjoys direct entry to the home as well as providing additional storage space.
Three generous, robed bedrooms & an immense master with walk-ins/ensuite are warmly carpeted in modern tones whilst stylish low maintenance floor coverings feature throughout the home minimizing maintenance and delivering durability should you consider this fine townhouse as a trouble-free investment opportunity.
Comprehensively serviced with appointments like Ducted heating/cooling, security system & door- camera as well as rainwater tank support, this is a walk-in worry free home with immediate lifestyle benefits minutes from Eastlink & public transport options.

Description:
Forget Building! This Home is Ready to Go!
Sitting in Dandenong’s newest estate Meridian, this almost brand-new home is perfect for families who desire a modern lifestyle and great accessibility to all amenities in every corner of Melbourne. Built on an above average lot size of 571 sqm the immaculate 4 bedroom home offers every possible feature you can think of including master suite with walk in robe and full en suite, 3 spacious living areas that are ideal for entertaining family and friends and giving your kids their own space in the home, open plan kitchen and meals area that overlook the beautiful parklands at the rear of the home, double lock up garage with remote access and direct internal access as well as at least 4 additional off street car spaces at the front and a magnificent rear alfresco which is sure to provide a perfect setting for barbeques during the coming summer months. Additionally the fully equipped home comes with an array of features including central gas ducted heating, evaporative cooling, downlights through living, meals and kitchen areas, loads of storage space throughout entire home including walk in pantry in kitchen, contemporary stainless steel appliances in kitchen, high speed internet with fibre to the home connection, high ceilings and an abundance of natural light throughout entire home and lots, lots more. With impressive natural surroundings through its beautifully set out front landscaping and an amazing rear parkland that includes walking track, kid’s playground and barbeque area this home provides everything that a modern family home should have. Do not walk past this once in a lifetime opportunity to purchase in Dandenong’s most sought after estate! Make sure you view this home before it is someone else’s!

Description:
Investors dream or FH buyer's entry
Situated in popular "Metro Village" is this unique park facing double story townhouse residence, brimful of natural light and inspiring interiors and exteriors.
With no Body Corp (Owners Corporation) fee and approximately 5 minutes' walk to Dandenong train station and bus stop, this is a great investment for investors as well as for first home buyers and small families who desire low maintenance living.
- Tailored for secure low-maintenance living, the property comprises an expansive open plan living, dining and kitchen zone, 3 good sized bedrooms (main bedroom with two-way access to en-suite) including second bedroom with balcony and park views and third bedroom on ground floor. There is also a computer nook/study area on the first level
- Kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances, dishwasher and plenty of cupboard space. Additional modern features, which include split system air conditioning, security alarm system and easy to look after rear courtyard
- Other features include single garage with remote control, large outdoor entertaining area, separate powder room, super-fast NBN fiber to the home internet, heating & cooling system & energy efficient lighting
- Location at its best with short proximity to train station, bus stops, parks with free BBQ area, Parkmore shopping centre, Springers Leisure Centre, Dandenong Market & Plaza
- Easy access to East Link, Dandenong Bypass, Princes Highway, South Gippsland Highway & Monash Freeway
This effortlessly stylish, well maintained home offers contemporary lifestyle in a central location. This remarkably versatile property will suit many buyers and is sure to impress, enquire now with Naval on 0401 489 262.

This property is one of the last remaining development opportunities on James Street and comes onto the market for sale for the first time in 40 years. Sitting on a land area of 647sqm (approx.), in a General Residential Zone – Sch 1 (Greater Dandenong Planning Scheme), this property allows for an astute developer/builder to build units/townhouses with a maximum return (STCA). Located in one of central Dandenong’s most sought after and premium pocket, this home is perfectly positioned with walking access to Dandenong High/Primary School, Dandenong Hospital, Chisholm TAFE and public transport services. With an existing weatherboard dwelling that offers 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, formal lounge area and separate kitchen/meals area, you can generate a rental yield whilst drawing plans and obtaining permits to build your next project (STCA). Large backyard and bonus outside living area with kitchenette and small living area. You need to see it to be able to believe it. The resale value of newly constructed units and townhouses in this area is also something to consider with this project, as this pocket is generally known for fetching premiums on newly constructed homes. This opportunity is presented once in a lifetime and could be your nest egg for the next 30 years! Do not wait until it is gone. Make sure you view this property now!

Description:
SIMPLY RENOVATED MASTERPIECE
Welcoming you to this beautifully renovated and low maintenance apartment that is stylish, cosy and in a perfect location within walking distance to Dandenong Plaza Shopping Centre, Dandenong North Primary school, Dandenong High School, Dandenong Hospital and public transport.
Enter this inviting modern home and you are greeted with a floor-boarded, light filled lounge room with an electric wall heater and tinted blinds giving you the privacy you need. This is overlooked by the hostess kitchen with a stone bench top as well as all new stainless-steel appliances and a gas burner cook top.
A generous sized bedroom comes with a built-in wardrobe that is nearby to the bathroom featuring a large mirror, vanity, toilet and a laundry section with storage space.
Perfect for those looking to down size or are wanting to purchase their first home.
